#: model:ir.model.fields,help:base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation.field_wua_invoicing_configuration_invoicing_based_on_wc
msgid "If enabled, invoicing will be based only on water connections, parcels will be ignored"
msgstr "Si se activa, cada factura estará referida a una toma, y se asumirá que todas las parcelas de la toma tienen el mismo pagador de agua"

#. module: base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation.field_wua_invoicing_configuration_apply_min_consumption_threshold_per_wc
msgid "If enabled, when consumptions are grouped per water connection, those water connections whose total consumption is below the threshold will be excluded from invoicing (consumptions will remain available for future invoice sets)."
msgstr "Si se activa, cuando los consumos se agrupan por toma, las tomas cuyo consumo total este por debajo del umbral quedaran excluidas de la facturacion (los consumos quedaran disponibles para futuros lotes de facturas)."

#. module: base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation.field_wua_invoiceset_line_min_consumption_threshold_per_wc
msgid "If global parameter \"Apply min. consumption threshold per WC\" is enabled, the consumptions grouped per water connection whose total consumption is below this threshold will not be invoiced. Use 0 to disable the threshold for this line."
msgstr "Si el parametro global \"Aplicar umbral min. de consumo por toma\" esta activado, los consumos agrupados por toma cuyo consumo total este por debajo de este umbral no se facturaran. Use 0 para desactivar el umbral en esta linea."

#. module: base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:base_wua_invoicing_pressurized_irrigation.field_wua_invoicing_configuration_print_consumption_section
